 ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
 CONFIGURATION SECTION.
 SPECIAL-NAMES.
* If SWITCH-15 is set (using a PARAM command), additional information will
* be displayed. This is used for debugging by SSG and development.
     SWITCH-15 SWITCH15 ON DEBUG-MODE
     FILE "=COBOLLIB" COBOLLIB
     FILE "=CBL85UTL" CBL85UTL
     FILE "OTALNAME"  OTALNAME
     SYMBOLIC HEX-FE 255
     CLASS COMMENT-CHARS           " !\"
     CLASS WC-FILENAME             " $*?" "0" THRU "9" "A" THRU "Z"
     CLASS NODE-NAME               " \"   "0" THRU "9" "A" THRU "Z"
     CLASS VALID-CATEGORY-TYPES    "DFLORSTZ"
     CLASS VALID-TRANSACTION-TYPES "BXQ".
*----------------------------------------------------------------------------
 INPUT-OUTPUT SECTION.
 FILE-CONTROL.
     SELECT OPTIONAL CONTROL-FILE ASSIGN #DYNAMIC
            RESERVE 8
            FILE STATUS IS CONTROL-FILE-STATUS.
     SELECT CSV-FILE     ASSIGN #DYNAMIC.
* The RESERVE cluase is not specified in this case since it is ignored for
* EDIT files (Don Nelson).
     SELECT SORT-FILE    ASSIGN #TEMP.
     SELECT SPOOLER-FILE ASSIGN #DYNAMIC.
 I-O-CONTROL.
     SAME CONTROL-FILE CSV-FILE SPOOLER-FILE.
