 3415-10-SEARCH-ALL-PROCESS.
     SEARCH ALL PROCESS-TABLE
         END
*        When no link is found, we set PROCESS-INDEX to zero
             SET PROCESS-INDEX TO ZERO
         WHEN PROCESS-CPU-NUM (PROCESS-INDEX) =
                  OPENER-CPU OF DISCOPEN-DEFINITION AND
                  PROCESS-PIN     (PROCESS-INDEX) =
                  OPENER-PIN OF DISCOPEN-DEFINITION AND
                  PROCESS-UNIQUE  (PROCESS-INDEX) = ZERO
