 3415-50-TREAT-CONTINUED.
* Determine the corresponding TITLE-INDEX
     IF PROCESS-INDEX = ZERO
*        This means no link was found, so discopen information should go
*        to process category 99
         SET TITLE-INDEX TO TITLE-MAX
         ADD 1 TO NUMBER-UNLINKED-DISCOPENS
     ELSE
         ADD 1 TO NUMBER-LINKED-DISCOPENS
         SEARCH ALL TITLE-TABLE
             END
*                This should never happen ...
                 STRING COMPLETION-56  DELIMITED SIZE
                        " (no title) " DELIMITED SIZE
                        INTO COMPLETION-MESSAGE
                 MOVE 1 TO ABEND-REQUIRED-FLAG
                 PERFORM 9010-SPCOMPLETION
             WHEN TITLE-NUMBER OF TITLE-TABLE (TITLE-INDEX) =
                  PROCESS-WKLD-NUMBER (PROCESS-INDEX)
                 NEXT SENTENCE
         END-SEARCH
     END-IF.
* DRIVER-INPUT-CALLS, DRIVER-OUTPUT-CALLS, CACHE-HITS, CACHE-WRITE-HITS can
* be negative since original counters are unsigned
     IF DRIVER-INPUT-CALLS  OF DISCOPEN-DEFINITION NEGATIVE OR
        DRIVER-OUTPUT-CALLS OF DISCOPEN-DEFINITION NEGATIVE OR
        CACHE-HITS          OF DISCOPEN-DEFINITION NEGATIVE OR
        CACHE-WRITE-HITS    OF DISCOPEN-DEFINITION NEGATIVE
         STRING COMPLETION-56                   DELIMITED SIZE
                " (DISCOPEN counters negative)" DELIMITED SIZE
                INTO COMPLETION-MESSAGE
         MOVE 1 TO ABEND-REQUIRED-FLAG
         PERFORM 9010-SPCOMPLETION
     END-IF.
* Add discopen counters TO CSV-W-BINARY
     ADD CACHE-HITS       OF DISCOPEN-DEFINITION
         CACHE-WRITE-HITS OF DISCOPEN-DEFINITION
         TO W06 OF CSV-W-BINARY (TITLE-INDEX)
         ON SIZE ERROR
         MOVE MAX-VALUE-19 TO W06 OF CSV-W-BINARY (TITLE-INDEX).
     COMPUTE W07 OF CSV-W-BINARY (TITLE-INDEX)                    =
         W07 OF CSV-W-BINARY (TITLE-INDEX)                        +
         DRIVER-INPUT-CALLS  OF DISCOPEN-DEFINITION +
         DRIVER-OUTPUT-CALLS OF DISCOPEN-DEFINITION -
         CACHE-HITS          OF DISCOPEN-DEFINITION -
         CACHE-WRITE-HITS    OF DISCOPEN-DEFINITION
         ON SIZE ERROR
         MOVE MAX-VALUE-19 TO W07 OF CSV-W-BINARY (TITLE-INDEX)
     END-COMPUTE.
* Index the file name into VOLUME-TABLE to get the basic read and write costs
* and disc-to-discopen ratio
     SEARCH ALL VOLUME-TABLE
         END
* Soln 10-010627-1347. Added the binary SEARCH below, to accommodate virtual
* disks for SMF. The DEVICE-NAME field contains the device location of the
* physical file corresponding to the logical file name of the SMF file. It is
* used here to index into the VOLUME-TABLE, when the outer SEARCH with VOLUME
* field (which is blank for SMF files) fails to find a match. Changes begin:
         SEARCH ALL VOLUME-TABLE
            END
*              This should never occur !
               STRING COMPLETION-56    DELIMITED SIZE
                    " (VOLUME LINK)" DELIMITED SIZE
                    INTO COMPLETION-MESSAGE
               MOVE 1 TO ABEND-REQUIRED-FLAG
               PERFORM 9010-SPCOMPLETION
          WHEN VOLUME-SYSTEM-NUMBER (VOLUME-INDEX) = SYSTEM-INDEX-2 AND
               VOLUME-NAME (VOLUME-INDEX) = DEVICE-NAME OF DISCOPEN-DEFINITION
                     PERFORM 3415-60-COMPUTE-A
                IF NO-OF-VOLUME-RECS(VOLUME-INDEX) NOT >
                    (NO-OF-FILES(VOLUME-INDEX) * 4)
*               In this case the volume is unmirrored
                    PERFORM 3415-70-COMPUTE-B
                ELSE
*                When the volume is mirrored, the number of writes and
*                write seconds must be doubled
                   PERFORM 3415-80-COMPUTE-C
                END-IF
         END-SEARCH
* Soln 10-010627-1347. Changes end here.
         WHEN VOLUME-SYSTEM-NUMBER (VOLUME-INDEX) = SYSTEM-INDEX-2 AND
              VOLUME-NAME (VOLUME-INDEX) =
              VOLUME OF DISCOPEN-DEFINITION
                  PERFORM 3415-60-COMPUTE-A
             IF NO-OF-VOLUME-RECS(VOLUME-INDEX) NOT >
                 (NO-OF-FILES(VOLUME-INDEX) * 4)
*                in this case the volume is unmirrored
                    PERFORM 3415-70-COMPUTE-B
             ELSE
