 4015-MAIN-PRINT.
* If new process category name detected, print totals
     IF SORT-WKLD-NAME NOT = PREVIOUS-WKLD-NAME AND
         PREVIOUS-WKLD-NAME NOT = SPACES
         PERFORM 4050-PRINT-TOTAL
     END-IF.
* Move fields to detail line
     EVALUATE TRUE
         WHEN SORT-WKLD-NAME NOT = PREVIOUS-WKLD-NAME OR FORCE-FULL-LINE
             PERFORM 4021-PRINT-A
         WHEN SORT-SYSTEM-NAME NOT = PREVIOUS-SYSTEM-NAME
             PERFORM 4022-PRINT-B
         WHEN SORT-VOLUME NOT = PREVIOUS-VOLUME
             PERFORM 4023-PRINT-C
         WHEN SORT-SUBVOLUME NOT = PREVIOUS-SUBVOLUME
             PERFORM 4024-PRINT-D
