             PERFORM 4025-PRINT-E
         WHEN SORT-PROCESS-NAME NOT = PREVIOUS-PROCESS-NAME
             PERFORM 4026-PRINT-F
         WHEN SORT-CPU-NUM NOT = PREVIOUS-CPU-NUM
             PERFORM 4027-PRINT-G
         WHEN SORT-PIN NOT = PREVIOUS-PIN
             PERFORM 4028-PRINT-H
         WHEN OTHER
             PERFORM 4029-PRINT-I
     END-EVALUATE.
     DIVIDE SORT-CPU-BUSY-TIME BY 1000000 GIVING P-CPU-BUSY-TIME.
     DIVIDE SORT-DELTA-TIME    BY 1000000 GIVING P-DELTA-TIME.
     ADD  SORT-CPU-BUSY-TIME TO TOTAL-CPU-BUSY-TIME.
* Print detail line
     WRITE SPOOLER-FILE-RECORD FROM P-DETAIL AFTER ADVANCING-LINES
         EOP SET EOP-DETECTED TO TRUE.
     IF EOP-DETECTED
         PERFORM 4030-END-OF-PAGE
         PERFORM 4040-PRINT-TITLES
         SET NO-EOP-DETECTED TO TRUE
     ELSE
         MOVE 1 TO ADVANCING-LINES
