 4050-PRINT-TOTAL.
* Print total cpu busy time for process category
     DIVIDE TOTAL-CPU-BUSY-TIME BY 1000000 GIVING P-CPU-BUSY-TIME-TOTAL.
     WRITE SPOOLER-FILE-RECORD FROM P-TOTAL-1 AFTER ZERO.
     WRITE SPOOLER-FILE-RECORD FROM P-TOTAL-2
         EOP SET EOP-DETECTED TO TRUE.
     IF EOP-DETECTED
         IF NOT LAST-RECORD-RETURNED
             PERFORM 4030-END-OF-PAGE
             PERFORM 4040-PRINT-TITLES
         END-IF
         SET NO-EOP-DETECTED TO TRUE
     ELSE
         MOVE 2 TO ADVANCING-LINES
     END-IF.
     MOVE ZERO TO TOTAL-CPU-BUSY-TIME.
